India’s Subbarao Says Burden ‘Left to Central Banks’

-- B y   D r e w   B e n s o n
-- 
2011-09-26T16:29:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-26/india-s-subbarao-says-burden-left-to-central-banks-.html
Reserve Bank of India Governor
Duvvuri Subbarao said today that “the burden has been left to
central banks” as governments have been unable to stimulate
economies.  Subbarao was speaking at an event in  New York .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Drew Benson in Buenos Aires at 
